snippet.title: SHADOWVANE Gameplay (Open Alpha) - No Commentary [60 FPS]
snippet.description:
Shadowvane is a Soulslike MMO with a 1v1 PvP Arena, 5v5 Battlegrounds, and an Open World realm where players can interact and advance their character.

This footage is from Patch 1.0.6.

https://playshadowvane.com
